________________________________________

Solarus Quest Editor 1.4.0 (in progress)
________________________________________

The quest editor is being rewritten from scratch in C++/Qt.

New features
------------

* The quest can now be run from the editor.
* The quest tree now automatically refreshes after changes in the filesystem.
* Editor tabs now show an icon representing the kind of file opened.
* Show an appropriate icon in tabs.
* Show an asterisk in the tab of files that are changed.
* The window now shows the Solarus icon.

Missing features
----------------

The rewriting is currently in progress.
At this moment, it is in a very early stage, so almost everything that is
possible with the old editor is still to be done in the new one.

* Create a new quest.
* Add, remove or rename resources.
* Edit maps.
* Edit tilesets.
* Edit sprites.
* Upgrade quests to the latest format.

